Description: Claude plan usage MATE panel applet
 Displays Claude AI plan usage directly in the MATE panel,
 showing the 5-hour rolling window and weekly utilisation
 percentages with colour-coded indicators and reset times.
 .
 Fetches data from the Anthropic API using the OAuth credentials
 stored by Claude Code.
